Package: better
Title: Make guestimates about the impact of health nudges
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jan", "Lindemans", , "janwillem.lindemans@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-3702-8651"))
Description: Tell `better` what kind of behavioral nudge you are considering, and what disease you are targetting, and `better` will give you guestimates about its impact on reducing deaths and disability. It primarily uses data from the Global Burden of Disease study.
